      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a row-your-own 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This vehicle is mechanically impeccable, having undergone full preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis remains rigid with factory-spec bushings and an M-Variable limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the interior shows zero bolster wear and all electronics function to OEM specifications. This is a turn-key example for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and historical preservation.",
