      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true time capsule for the discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, showing absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every body panel is original, and the factory alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in an impeccable state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing rain or snow. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt from the date of purchase. All electronics, switches, and displays function exactly as they did the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawlessly maintained example that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new vehicle.",
